================================================================================
   PACKAGES
================================================================================

This software consists of five packages:
 - lprms-core	: Core system monitoring daemon
 - lprms-web	: Web portal/barebones CMS
 - lprms-signio	: Graphical Sign-in/out system
 - lprms-status	: Graphical system status display
 - lprms-docs	: Documentation

Each package can theoretically be installed and deployed without requiring
any of the others, however all of them have been created with a comprehensive, 
cohesive, software structure in mind.

